Veteran actor Sandy Mokoena has died. The New Age has confirmed with eTV’s Scandal that Mokoena (68) passed away on Thursday morning. According to eTV Mokwena had been sick since late last year and his cause of death was still being determined. Mokwena joined the popular soapie Scandal in 2005 playing the role of journalist “Bra Eddie”. He has also featured in various other popular productions including Generations and Yizo Yizo. South Africans have taken to social media to express their grief at the news of Mokwena’s passing. -TNA Reporter